mann]] | title=Modern Portfolio Theory and Investment Analysis (9th Edition)| publisher=[[John Wiley & Sons|Wiley]] | location= | year=2014| isbn=978-1118469941}}\n* {{cite book | author=Robert A. Haugen | title=Modern Investment Theory (5th Edition)| publisher= Prentice Hall | location= | year=2000| isbn=978-0130191700| author-link=Robert Haugen}}\n* {{cite book | author= [[Mark S. Joshi]], Jane M. Paterson | title=Introduction to Mathematical Portfolio Theory| publisher= Cambridge University Press | location= | year=2013| isbn=978-1107042315 }}\n* {{cite book | author=Lutz Kruschwitz, Andreas Loeffler | title=Discounted Cash Flow: A Theory of the Valuation of Firms | publisher=Wiley | location= | year=2005 | isbn=978-0470870440 | url=https://archive.org/details/discountedcashfl00krus }}\n* {{cite book | author= David G. Luenberger | title=Investment Science (2nd Edition)| publisher=[[Oxford University Press]] | location= | year=2013| isbn=978-0199740086| author-link=David Luenberger}}\n* {{cite book | author= Harry M. Markowitz | title=Portfolio Selection: Efficient Diversification of Investments (2nd Edition)| publisher= Wiley | location= | year=1991| isbn=978-1557861085 | author-link=Harry M. Markowitz}}\n* {{cite book | author= Frank Milne | title=Finance Theory and Asset Pricing (2nd Edition) | publisher= Oxford University Press | location= | year=2003| isbn=978-0199261079| author-link=Frank Milne }}\n* {{cite book | author= George Pennacchi | title=Theory of Asset Pricing| publisher= Prentice Hall | location= | year=2007| isbn=978-0321127204 | author-link=George Pennacchi}}\n* {{cite book | author= Mark Rubinstein | title=A History of the Theory of Investments| publisher= Wiley| location= | year=2006| isbn=978-0471770565| author-link=Mark Rubinstein}}\n* {{cite book | author= William F. Sharpe | title=Portfolio Theory and Capital Markets: The Original Edition| publisher= [[McGraw-Hill]] | location= | year=1999| isbn=978-0071353205| author-link=William F. Shar