{"title_page": "Avelia", "text_new": "{{short description|Genus of protists in the ciliates phylum}}\n\n{{About|a unicellular organism|the high-speed train|Euroduplex{{!}}Avelia}}\n\n{{Automatic taxobox \n| image = \n| image_upright = \n| image_caption = \n| display_parents = 4\n| taxon = Avelia\n| authority = Nouzar\u00e8de, 1977\n| subdivision_ranks = Species\n| subdivision = \n* ''A. arcachonense'' <small>(Nouzar\u00e8de 1975) Nouzar\u00e8de 1977</small>\n* ''A. gigas'' <small>(Dragesco 1954) Nouzar\u00e8de 1977</small>\n* ''A. martinicense'' <small>(Nouzar\u00e8de 1975) Nouzar\u00e8de 1977</small>\n* ''A. multinucleata'' <small>Dragesco 1999</small>\n}}\n\n'''''Avelia''''' is a genus of karyorelict ciliates belonging to the family Geleiidae.<ref name=\"Dragesco1999\">{{Cite journal |last=Dragesco |first=Jean |date=26 November 1999 |title=R\u00e9vision des Gel\u00e9iides (Ciliophora, Karyorelictea) |url=http://www.zobodat.at/pdf/STAPFIA_0066_0001-0091.pdf |journal=Stapfia |volume=66 |pages=1\u201391 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.marinespecies.org/aphia.php?p=taxdetails&id=425699 |title=WoRMS \u2013 World Register of Marine Species \u2013 Avelia Nouzar\u00e8de, 1977 |website=www.marinespecies.org |access-date=2020-04-05 }}</ref>\n\nThe genus name is a [[Patronym (taxonomy)#Naming process|taxonomic patronyms]] honoring Marcel Avel (1900\u20131983; professor of anatomy),<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://cths.fr/an/savant.php?id=118037 |title=Comit\u00e9 des travaux historiques et scientifiques (CTHS) \u2013 AVEL Marcel |website=cths.fr |language=French |access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref> with slight modification into the ''[[nomen novum]]'' ''Avelia'' to avoid a taxonomic homonymy with the moth genus ''[[Avela]]''.<ref name=\"Dragesco1999\"/>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Alveolata}}\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q25363970}}\n\n[[Category:Karyorelictea]]\n[[Category:Ciliate genera]]\n[[Category:Taxa described in 1977]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Genus of protists in the ciliates phylum}}\n\n{{About|a unicellular organism|the high-speed train|Euroduplex{{!}}Avelia}}\n\n{{Automatic taxobox \n| image = \n| image_upright = \n| image_caption = \n| display_parents = 4\n| taxon = Avelia\n| authority = Nouzar\u00e8de, 1977\n| subdivision_ranks = Species\n| subdivision = \n* ''A. arcachonense'' <small>(Nouzar\u00e8de 1975) Nouzar\u00e8de 1977</small>\n* ''A. gigas'' <small>(Dragesco 1954) Nouzar\u00e8de 1977</small>\n* ''A. martinicense'' <small>(Nouzar\u00e8de 1975) Nouzar\u00e8de 1977</small>\n* ''A. multinucleata'' <small>Dragesco 1999</small>\n}}\n\n''Avelia'' is a genus of karyorelict ciliates belonging to the family Geleiidae.<ref name=\"Dragesco1999\">{{Cite journal |last=Dragesco |first=Jean |date=26 November 1999 |title=R\u00e9vision des Gel\u00e9iides (Ciliophora, Karyorelictea) |url=http://www.zobodat.at/pdf/STAPFIA_0066_0001-0091.pdf |journal=Stapfia |volume=66 |pages=1\u201391 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.marinespecies.org/aphia.php?p=taxdetails&id=425699 |title=WoRMS \u2013 World Register of Marine Species \u2013 Avelia Nouzar\u00e8de, 1977 |website=www.marinespecies.org |access-date=2020-04-05 }}</ref>\n\nThe genus name is a [[Patronym (taxonomy)#Naming process|taxonomic patronyms]] honoring Marcel Avel (1900\u20131983; professor of anatomy),<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://cths.fr/an/savant.php?id=118037 |title=Comit\u00e9 des travaux historiques et scientifiques (CTHS) \u2013 AVEL Marcel |website=cths.fr |language=French |access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref> with slight modification into the ''[[nomen novum]]'' ''Avelia'' to avoid a taxonomic homonymy with the moth genus ''[[Avela]]''.<ref name=\"Dragesco1999\"/>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Alveolata}}\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q25363970}}\n\n[[Category:Karyorelictea]]\n[[Category:Ciliate genera]]\n[[Category:Taxa described in 1977]]\n", "name_user": "Manudouz", "label": "safe", "comment": "As perMOS:BOLDLEAD.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Avelia"}
